      "type": "html",
      "content": "<ArticlePage\r\n      title=\"Top Artists in the United States\"\r\n      subtitle=\"The biggest names dominating the music industry today\"\r\n      category=\"Music\"\r\n      lastUpdated=\"January 23, 2026\"\r\n      tableOfContents={tableOfContents}\r\n    >\r\n      <p class=\"text-xl font-medium text-gray-700 mb-6 leading-relaxed\">\r\n        These are the <strong>top 7 artists</strong> currently dominating the \r\n        <strong>United States music scene</strong>. Based on streaming numbers,\r\n        chart performance, cultural impact, and industry influence, these\r\n        musicians represent the most significant forces in modern music.\r\n      </p>\r\n\r\n      <Section id=\"rankings\" title=\"Current Rankings\">\r\n        <p class=\"text-gray-700 mb-4\">\r\n          Rankings based on monthly streaming listeners, chart performance, and\r\n          cultural impact as of January 2026:\r\n        </p>\r\n\r\n        <DataTable\r\n          headers={[\"Rank\", \"Artist\", \"Genre\", \"Monthly Listeners\", \"Key Achievement\"]}\r\n          rows={[\r\n            [\"1\", \"Taylor Swift\", \"Pop / Country\", \"95M+\", \"Eras Tour Record Holder\"],\r\n            [\"2\", \"The Weeknd\", \"R&B / Pop\", \"90M+\", \"Blinding Lights Diamond\"],\r\n            [\"3\", \"Drake\", \"Hip-Hop / R&B\", \"85M+\", \"Most Streamed All-Time\"],\r\n            [\"4\", \"Bad Bunny\", \"Latin Trap\", \"78M+\", \"Global Streaming Leader\"],\r\n            [\"5\", \"SZA\", \"R&B / Soul\", \"65M+\", \"SOS Album Phenomenon\"],\r\n            [\"6\", \"Peso Pluma\", \"Regional Mexican\", \"52M+\", \"Corridos Tumbados Pioneer\"],\r\n            [\"7\", \"Yeat\", \"Rage Rap\", \"42M+\", \"Underground to Mainstream\"],\r\n          ]}\r\n        />\r\n      </Section>\r\n\r\n      <Section id=\"profiles\" title=\"Artist Profiles\">\r\n        <div class=\"grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6 mb-8\">\r\n          \r\n          <a\r\n            href=\"/artists/taylor-swift\"\r\n            class=\"block bg-gradient-to-br from-purple-50 to-pink-50 rounded-xl p-6 border-2 border-purple-200 hover:border-purple-400 transition-colors\"\r\n          >\r\n            <div class=\"flex items-center justify-between mb-3\">\r\n              <span class=\"text-4xl\">👑</span>\r\n              <span class=\"text-xs font-bold text-purple-600 bg-purple-100 px-2 py-1 rounded\">#1</span>\r\n            </div>\r\n            <h3 class=\"text-xl font-black text-gray-900 mb-2\">Taylor Swift</h3>\r\n            <p class=\"text-sm text-gray-600 mb-2\">Pop / Country</p>\r\n            <p class=\"text-2xl font-bold text-purple-600 mb-2\">95M+</p>\r\n            <p class=\"text-xs text-gray-700\">14x Grammy Winner, Eras Tour Record Holder</p>\r\n          </a>\r\n\r\n          \r\n          <a\r\n            href=\"/artists/the-weeknd\"\r\n            class=\"block bg-gradient-to-br from-red-50 to-gray-50 rounded-xl p-6 border-2 border-red-200 hover:border-red-400 transition-colors\"\r\n          >\r\n            <div class=\"flex items-center justify-between mb-3\">\r\n              <span class=\"text-4xl\">🌙</span>\r\n              <span class=\"text-xs font-bold text-red-600 bg-red-100 px-2 py-1 rounded\">#2</span>\r\n            </div>\r\n            <h3 class=\"text-xl font-black text-gray-900 mb-2\">The Weeknd</h3>\r\n            <p class=\"text-sm text-gray-600 mb-2\">R&B / Pop</p>\r\n            <p class=\"text-2xl font-bold text-red-600 mb-2\">90M+</p>\r\n            <p class=\"text-xs text-gray-700\">4x Grammy Winner, Multiple Diamond Certifications</p>\r\n          </a>\r\n\r\n          \r\n          <a\r\n            href=\"/artists/drake\"\r\n            class=\"block bg-gradient-to-br from-yellow-50 to-orange-50 rounded-xl p-6 border-2 border-yellow-200 hover:border-yellow-400 transition-colors\"\r\n          >\r\n            <div class=\"flex items-center justify-between mb-3\">\r\n              <span class=\"text-4xl\">🦉</span>\r\n              <span class=\"text-xs font-bold text-yellow-600 bg-yellow-100 px-2 py-1 rounded\">#3</span>\r\n            </div>\r\n            <h3 class=\"text-xl font-black text-gray-900 mb-2\">Drake</h3>\r\n            <p class=\"text-sm text-gray-600 mb-2\">Hip-Hop / R&B</p>\r\n            <p class=\"text-2xl font-bold text-yellow-600 mb-2\">85M+</p>\r\n            <p class=\"text-xs text-gray-700\">5x Grammy Winner, Most Streamed Artist Ever</p>\r\n          </a>\r\n\r\n          \r\n          <a\r\n            href=\"/artists/bad-bunny\"\r\n            class=\"block bg-gradient-to-br from-pink-50 to-yellow-50 rounded-xl p-6 border-2 border-pink-200 hover:border-pink-400 transition-colors\"\r\n          >\r\n            <div class=\"flex items-center justify-between mb-3\">\r\n              <span class=\"text-4xl\">🐰</span>\r\n              <span class=\"text-xs font-bold text-pink-600 bg-pink-100 px-2 py-1 rounded\">#4</span>\r\n            </div>\r\n            <h3 class=\"text-xl font-black text-gray-900 mb-2\">Bad Bunny</h3>\r\n            <p class=\"text-sm text-gray-600 mb-2\">Latin Trap / Reggaeton</p>\r\n            <p class=\"text-2xl font-bold text-pink-600 mb-2\">78M+</p>\r\n            <p class=\"text-xs text-gray-700\">3x Grammy Winner, Global Streaming Leader 2020-2022</p>\r\n          </a>\r\n\r\n          \r\n          <a\r\n            href=\"/artists/sza\"\r\n            class=\"block bg-gradient-to-br from-teal-50 to-blue-50 rounded-xl p-6 border-2 border-teal-200 hover:border-teal-400 transition-colors\"\r\n          >\r\n            <div class=\"flex items-center justify-between mb-3\">\r\n              <span class=\"text-4xl\">🌊</span>\r\n              <span class=\"text-xs font-bold text-teal-600 bg-teal-100 px-2 py-1 rounded\">#5</span>\r\n            </div>\r\n            <h3 class=\"text-xl font-black text-gray-900 mb-2\">SZA</h3>\r\n            <p class=\"text-sm text-gray-600 mb-2\">R&B / Soul</p>\r\n            <p class=\"text-2xl font-bold text-teal-600 mb-2\">65M+</p>\r\n            <p class=\"text-xs text-gray-700\">4x Grammy Winner, SOS Album Phenomenon</p>\r\n          </a>\r\n\r\n          \r\n          <a\r\n            href=\"/artists/peso-pluma\"\r\n            class=\"block bg-gradient-to-br from-green-50 to-red-50 rounded-xl p-6 border-2 border-green-200 hover:border-green-400 transition-colors\"\r\n          >\r\n            <div class=\"flex items-center justify-between mb-3\">\r\n              <span class=\"text-4xl\">🪶</span>\r\n              <span class=\"text-xs font-bold text-green-600 bg-green-100 px-2 py-1 rounded\">#6</span>\r\n            </div>\r\n            <h3 class=\"text-xl font-black text-gray-900 mb-2\">Peso Pluma</h3>\r\n            <p class=\"text-sm text-gray-600 mb-2\">Regional Mexican</p>\r\n            <p class=\"text-2xl font-bold text-green-600 mb-2\">52M+</p>\r\n            <p class=\"text-xs text-gray-700\">Latin Grammy Winner, Corridos Tumbados Pioneer</p>\r\n          </a>\r\n\r\n          \r\n          <a\r\n            href=\"/artists/yeat\"\r\n            class=\"block bg-gradient-to-br from-red-50 to-gray-50 rounded-xl p-6 border-2 border-red-200 hover:border-red-400 transition-colors\"\r\n          >\r\n            <div class=\"flex items-center justify-between mb-3\">\r\n              <span class=\"text-4xl\">🔔</span>\r\n              <span class=\"text-xs font-bold text-red-600 bg-red-100 px-2 py-1 rounded\">#7</span>\r\n            </div>\r\n            <h3 class=\"text-xl font-black text-gray-900 mb-2\">Yeat</h3>\r\n            <p class=\"text-sm text-gray-600 mb-2\">Rage Rap / Hip-Hop</p>\r\n            <p class=\"text-2xl font-bold text-red-600 mb-2\">42M+</p>\r\n            <p class=\"text-xs text-gray-700\">Billboard 200 #1, Viral Streaming Phenomenon</p>\r\n          </a>\r\n        </div>\r\n      </Section>\r\n\r\n      <Section id=\"trends\" title=\"Industry Trends\">\r\n        <h3 class=\"text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3\">Key Observations</h3>\r\n        <ul class=\"list-disc list-inside text-gray-700 space-y-2 mb-4\">\r\n          <li>\r\n            <strong>Streaming Dominance:</strong> Monthly listeners continue to\r\n            be the primary metric of success\r\n          </li>\r\n          <li>\r\n            <strong>Genre Diversity:</strong> Top artists span pop, hip-hop, R&B,\r\n            Latin, and regional Mexican music\r\n          </li>\r\n          <li>\r\n            <strong>Global Influence:</strong> International artists (Bad Bunny,\r\n            Peso Pluma) breaking through in the US\r\n          </li>\r\n          <li>\r\n            <strong>Underground to Mainstream:</strong> Artists like Yeat proving\r\n            viral success can translate to mainstream dominance\r\n          </li>\r\n          <li>\r\n            <strong>Tour Revenue:</strong> Live performances driving massive\r\n            revenue (Taylor Swifts Eras Tour)\r\n          </li>\r\n        </ul>\r\n      </Section>\r\n    </ArticlePage>"
    }
  ],
